Create the World:
    Initialize the window with given dimensions
    Build a Board / initialize tiles according to dimensions

    Tiles -> Mode (Empty, Obstacle, Search Expore, Seach Selected, )
    Mode determines colouring and inner attributes


The algortihm and running options (if any) are selected in the menu

The Application class is taking care of running the algortihms


The Algorithm is Creating it's own Game (Player) instances and handles rendering, updates.